### Banking Transactions API - Test Requests
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension or similar HTTP client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@accountId = ACC123
@accountId2 = ACC456

### ============================================
### TRANSACTIONS
### ============================================

### Create a deposit transaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "{{accountId}}",
  "amount": 1000,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}

### Create another deposit
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "{{accountId}}",
  "amount": 500,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}

### Create a withdrawal transaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "{{accountId}}",
  "amount": 200,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "withdrawal"
}

### Create a transfer transaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "{{accountId}}",
  "toAccount": "{{accountId2}}",
  "amount": 150,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "transfer"
}

### Get all transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions

### Get transactions filtered by account
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?accountId={{accountId}}

### Get transactions filtered by type
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?type=deposit

### Get transactions filtered by date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?from=2024-01-01&to=2026-12-31

### Get transactions with multiple filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?accountId={{accountId}}&type=deposit

### Export transactions as CSV
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/export?format=csv

### ============================================
### ACCOUNTS
### ============================================

### Get account balance
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/{{accountId}}/balance

### Get account summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/{{accountId}}/summary

### Calculate interest (5% rate, 30 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/{{accountId}}/interest?rate=0.05&days=30

### Calculate interest (10% rate, 365 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/{{accountId}}/interest?rate=0.10&days=365

### ============================================
### ERROR CASES
### ============================================

### Invalid transaction - missing required fields
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 100
}

### Account not found
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/NONEXISTENT/summary

### Invalid date format
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?from=invalid-date

### Missing format parameter for export
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/export

### Invalid interest parameters
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/{{accountId}}/interest?rate=-1&days=abc
